{"tha-ap10:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap10:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap10:0.3":"Pindolabharadvajattheraapadana ","tha-ap10:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap10:1.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap10:1.3":"Purato himavantassa, ","tha-ap10:1.4":"cittakute vasi tada. ","tha-ap10:2.1":"Abhitarupo tatthasim, ","tha-ap10:2.2":"migaraja catukkamo; ","tha-ap10:2.3":"Tassa saddam sunitvana, ","tha-ap10:2.4":"vikkhambhanti bahujjana. ","tha-ap10:3.1":"Suphullam padumam gayha, ","tha-ap10:3.2":"upagacchim narasabham; ","tha-ap10:3.3":"Vutthitassa samadhimha, ","tha-ap10:3.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap10:4.1":"Catuddisam namassitva, ","tha-ap10:4.2":"buddhasettham naruttamam; ","tha-ap10:4.3":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap10:4.4":"sihanadam nadim aham. ","tha-ap10:5.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap10:5.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap10:5.3":"Sakasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap10:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap10:6.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap10:6.2":"Sabbe deva samagata; ","tha-ap10:6.3":"‘Agato vadatam settho, ","tha-ap10:6.4":"Dhammam sossama tam mayam’. ","tha-ap10:7.1":"Tesam hasaparetanam, ","tha-ap10:7.2":"purato lokanayako; ","tha-ap10:7.3":"Mama saddam pakittesi, ","tha-ap10:7.4":"dighadassi mahamuni. ","tha-ap10:8.1":"Yenidam padumam dinnam, ","tha-ap10:8.2":"sihanado ca nadito; ","tha-ap10:8.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap10:8.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap10:9.1":"Ito atthamake kappe, ","tha-ap10:9.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap10:9.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap10:9.4":"catudipamhi issaro. ","tha-ap10:10.1":"Karayissati issariyam, ","tha-ap10:10.2":"mahiya catusatthiya; ","tha-ap10:10.3":"Padumo nama namena, ","tha-ap10:10.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap10:11.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap10:11.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap10:11.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap10:11.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap10:12.1":"Pakasite pavacane, ","tha-ap10:12.2":"brahmabandhu bhavissati; ","tha-ap10:12.3":"Brahmanna abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap10:12.4":"pabbajissati tavade. ","tha-ap10:13.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap10:13.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap10:13.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap10:13.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap10:14.1":"Vijane pantaseyyamhi, ","tha-ap10:14.2":"valamigasamakule; ","tha-ap10:14.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap10:14.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap10:15.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap10:15.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap10:15.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap10:15.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap10:16.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pindolabharadvajo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap10:17.1":"Pindolabharadvajattherassapadanam atthamam. "}